---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="intro-wrapper">
    <h1 class="site-title">Out of Scope</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A journal of consequence, hype, interface, and failure.</p>

    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>
        <strong>Out of Scope</strong> is a real-time field journal for tracking the shifting terrain of mediated life. It documents system failures, interface politics, hype cycles, and institutional obsolescence—using the lens of <a href="https://consequencedesign.org" class="underline">Consequence Design</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is not a blog. Not a newsletter. Not a whitepaper graveyard. It’s where I map live hypotheses and friction points in our techno-social environment, piece by piece.
      </p>
      <p>
        If something felt off but didn’t quite make the news cycle, you’ll probably find it here.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6">
        <a href="/journal" class="journal-link">Read the latest journal entries →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .intro-wrapper {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 6rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .site-title {
    font-family: 'Martel', serif;
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f1f1f;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Martel', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    font-family: 'Martel', serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: #3a3a3a;
  }

  .journal-link {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1e40af;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .site-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
